<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5399991>
    dc:description "FIG. 3. — Leucaltis clathria Haeckel, 1872. Spicules of the sponge wall. Note the giant tetractine and triactines of the cortex, minute triactines and tetractines present in the choanosomal skeleton and sagittal triactines in the membrane delimiting the central atrial cavity. Scale bar: 80 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5399991/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

